PRIVACY
POLICY
(Last updated on May 22, 2018)
This
              Privacy Policy is designed to provide clarity about the personal
              information and data SNG Bilişim Yazılım Danışmanlık ve Pazarlama
              Dış Ticaret Limited Şirketi and/or any of its agents, consultants,
              employees, officers and directors (“SNG”, “its”, “our”, “we”)
              collect, how it is collected, why it is being processed, how and
              where it is used, how long it is being retained, and whether it is
              being shared with any other parties. By installing and playing a
              game or any other application provided by SNG on the Apple App
              Store, Google Play App Store, or Facebook, you give your explicit
              and informed consent to the processing of your personal
              information in accordance with this Privacy Policy and Terms of
              Service.
As per
              definition, “personal data is any information relating to an
              individual, whether it relates to his or her private, professional
              or public life. It can be anything from a name, a home address, a
              photo, an email address, bank details, posts on social networking
              websites, medical information, or a computer’s IP address.”
Information We Collect
SNG collects data from you, through your
              interactions with our games. SNG facilitates third-party
              advertisement, tracking and analytics services and these services
              also collect both non-personal and personal data.
First type
              of data we collect is the Process Data acquired through your
              direct interaction with our game. This data is related solely to
              your progress at our games and you cannot be personally identified
              through this type of data. Thus, this type of data is
              non-personal. Non-personal information includes technical
              information, behavioural data and statistical data. Also, we do
              not ask of you to submit any personal information at any of our
              games as they do not require registration. Third-party services
              might also collect non-personal information. Non-personal
              Information collected by third-parties may include the following
              technical information: type of operation system (e.g. Android,
              iOS, etc.), type of browser (e.g. Explorer, Firefox, Chrome,
              Safari, etc.), screen resolution (e.g. 800×600, 1024×768, etc.),
              language (e.g. English), device type (e.g. Galaxy, HTC, iPhone,
              etc.), geo-location – only general location may be collected.
However,
              third-party advertisement, tracking and analytics services that we
              use, and Google and Facebook, if you use your Google and Facebook
              accounts to play one of our games, may have access to personal
              information such as your device identifier, MAC address, IMEI,
              location (specific location where a given language is spoken),
              geo-location information, and IP address for the purpose of
              providing their services under their respective privacy policies.
              SNG does not have control over these third parties and has access,
              as provided by these services, to the collective, anonymous data.
Exceptions to
              majority of our games are Gin Rummy Online and Pişti Online games.
              As these games both require online interaction of real people,
              registration of users and retainment of collected information is
              necessary. At Gin Rummy Online, Game Sparks’ service is used. Only
              personal information collected at Gin Rummy Online are Facebook or
              Google identities, depending on login preference of the user,
              public profile information like friends list, profile picture and
              name of the user, and geo-location (city, country). At Pişti
              online, Facebook id, public profile information like list of
              friends, profile picture and name of the user are collected as
              data.
How Do We Collect Information
As mentioned, we work with third-party
              advertisement and analytics services. Below a concise list of such
              services, type of personal information they collect, and a link to
              their own Privacy Policies, if there is one is provided. Links to
              their own Privacy Policies are embedded on the name of each
              service provider. We might use one or more of these services at
              our different games.
