Updates to
              this Privacy Policy
We will
              post any adjustments to this Privacy Policy on this page, and the
              revised version will be effective when it is posted. If we
              materially change the ways in which we use or share Personal
              Information previously collected from you through our products, we
              will notify you through our product, by email, or other
              communication.